Properties.EnglishScriptText: [[I can't wait to start classes.]] I'm looking forward to meeting my professors and learning all I can at Hogwarts.
[[I can't wait to explore.]] I'm looking forward to exploring Hogwarts and the world beyond the castle and grounds.
[[Daring.]] A sense of adventure? I like to think that I'm not afraid of anything.
[[Curiosity.]] A desire to learn? I do enjoy a good puzzle. And I believe I have a ready mind.
[[Loyalty.]] A sense of loyalty? I believe myself to be a true friend. I know I value that trait in others.
[[Ambition.]] Is it ambition? I may seem single-minded, but it is important to go after what you want from life.
